                    {
                        "title": "Learn",
                        "link": "setup-disguise-test-open"
                    }
                ],
                "content": "<p>Panic Button stays hidden on your phone by looking like a simple calculator. From now on, you will see the calculator disguise whenever you open the app. You will need to learn how to unlock the disguise to stop the automatic sending of the alert every 5 minutes. Learn how it works. </p>"
            },
            {
                "id": "setup-contacts",
                "lang": "en",
                "type": "interactive",
                "title": "Setup contacts",
                "introduction": "These people will receive the alert every 5 minutes if you activate it.",
                "warning": "They should know you personally and be able to respond fast.",
                "component": "contacts",
                "action": [
                    {
                        "title": "Next",
                        "link": "setup-message"
                    }
                ],
                "content": "<p>Security Tips</p><ul><li>Think about who can practically assist you - there is no point someone knowing you are in trouble if they cannot help. </li><li>Make a plan with your chosen contacts so that they are prepared to act fast. </li><li>Be aware of the risks - how might your contact be put at risk? </li></ul>"
            },
